msgstr "AgentNode"

#: ../../source/UserGuide/agent/agent_node.rst:5
msgid "概述"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../source/UserGuide/agent/agent_node.rst:7
msgid ":py:class:`~evofabric.core.agent.AgentNode` 是 EvoFabric 中的智能体节点，继承自 :py:class:`~evofabric.core.graph.AsyncStreamNode`，集成了 **记忆管理**、**工具调用**、**LLM 调用** 和 **输入输出格式化** 功能。 它适用于需要自然语言交互、状态追踪以及工具操作的复杂工作流场景。"
msgstr ":py:class:`~evofabric.core.agent.AgentNode` is the agent node in EvoFabric, inheriting from :py:class:`~evofabric.core.graph.AsyncStreamNode`, and integrates **memory management**, **tool calls**, **LLM calls**, and **input/output formatting**. It is suitable for complex workflow scenarios requiring natural language interaction, state tracking, and tool operations."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/agent/agent_node.rst:10
msgid "**工作流程：**"
msgstr "**Workflow:**"

#: ../../source/UserGuide/agent/agent_node.rst:12
msgid "调用记忆模块的 :py:meth:`~evofabric.core.mem.MemBase.retrieval_update` ，按顺序更新上下文状态。"
msgstr "Call the memory module's :py:meth:`~evofabric.core.mem.MemBase.retrieval_update` to sequentially update the context state."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/agent/agent_node.rst:13
msgid "使用 ``input_msg_format`` 模板，将输入状态格式化为 LLM 可识别的消息。"
msgstr "Use the ``input_msg_format`` template to format the input state into messages recognizable by LLM."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/agent/agent_node.rst:14
msgid "调用 :py:class:`~evofabric.core.clients.ChatClientBase` 执行推理，获取初步回复。"
msgstr "Call :py:class:`~evofabric.core.clients.ChatClientBase` to perform inference and obtain the preliminary response."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/agent/agent_node.rst:15
msgid "根据需要调用工具管理器执行相关操作。"
msgstr "Invoke the tool manager as needed to perform the relevant operations."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/agent/agent_node.rst:16
msgid "使用 ``output_msg_format`` 模板将 LLM 回复渲染为最终输出。"
msgstr "Use the ``output_msg_format`` template to render the LLM response into the final output."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/agent/agent_node.rst:17
msgid "调用记忆模块的 :py:meth:`~evofabric.core.mem.MemBase.add_messages` 按顺序更新记忆。"
msgstr "Call the memory module's :py:meth:`~evofabric.core.mem.MemBase.add_messages` to update the memory in order."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/agent/agent_node.rst:20
msgid "特性"
msgstr "Characteristics"

#: ../../source/UserGuide/agent/agent_node.rst:22
msgid "**集成记忆管理**：可同时管理多个记忆组件，实现上下文追踪。"
msgstr "**Integrated Memory Management**: Can simultaneously manage multiple memory components, enabling context tracking."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/agent/agent_node.rst:23
msgid "**工具调用支持**：可在推理过程中动态调用注册的工具。"
msgstr "**Tool Call Support**: Registered tools can be dynamically invoked during the reasoning process."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/agent/agent_node.rst:24
msgid "**LLM 推理封装**：统一管理输入格式化、推理参数和输出渲染。"
msgstr "**LLM Inference Encapsulation**: Unified management of input formatting, inference parameters, and output rendering."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/agent/agent_node.rst:25
msgid "**流式输出**：通过 :py:class:`~evofabric.core.graph.StreamWriter` 实现逐步输出 LLM 回复。"
msgstr "**Streaming Output**: Implemented via :py:class:`~evofabric.core.graph.StreamWriter` for step-by-step output of LLM responses."

#: ../../source/UserGuide/agent/agent_node.rst:26
msgid "**Pydantic 输出验证**：支持 ``output_schema`` 对 LLM 输出进行结构化校验。"
msgstr "**Pydantic Output Validation**: Supports ``output_schema`` for structured validation of LLM outputs."

